    <string name="help_title">Help</string>
    <string name="help_content">Welcome to Destinumber!\n\nThis app generates daily predictions using the leaked formulas of Robert Ofl, a US scientist from the 1960s who hypothesized that machines could predict the future based on patterns embedded in the universe\'s creation.\n\n## How it works:\n\nYour destiny number is calculated from your name, surname, and date of birth. Based on this number and the selected date, the app calculates 9 "cards" with your daily destiny written on the back.\n\n## Usage Rules:\n\n• 3 prediction attempts per day (reset at 03:00 UTC+3)\n• Predictions can be made up to 3 weeks in advance\n• One prediction per date (cannot be cancelled or deleted)\n\n## Getting Started:\n\n1. Create an account or log in\n2. Navigate to Destiny Cards\n3. Select a date and draw a card\n4. View your prediction history\n5. Update your profile information\n\nNote: This is a humorous app - all coincidences are random!</string>
